  <div class="slide" data-slide="2"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-60px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:250px;height:250px;bottom:-40px;left:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-8 reveal">Agenda</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-lg"><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">01</div><div>Problem context and hydrogen economy</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">02</div><div>Literature insights and existing gaps</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">03</div><div>Proposed system architecture and modules</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">04</div><div>Database, algorithms and Java implementation</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">05</div><div>Testing, outputs, benefits and limits</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-accent-1 font-bold mb-2">06</div><div>Future scope and conclusion</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="3"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:390px;height:390px;top:-70px;right:-90px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:260px;height:260px;bottom:-80px;left:-50px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.07"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Why green hydrogen?</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-5"><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">⚡</div><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Renewable powered</h3><p class="text-text-secondary mini">Green hydrogen is produced by water electrolysis using renewable electricity such as solar and wind.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🧩</div><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Energy bridge</h3><p class="text-text-secondary mini">It converts intermittent renewable power into a storable fuel for industry, mobility and long-duration backup.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌍</div><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Low carbon route</h3><p class="text-text-secondary mini">Integrated green hydrogen plants target zero fossil input in the hydrogen supply chain.</p></div></div><div class="mt-6 text-lg text-text-secondary reveal">A green hydrogen plant combines renewable generation, water treatment, electrolyzer stacks, storage, power conditioning and digital control in one coordinated system.</div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="4"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:320px;height:320px;top:-50px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.07"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-40px;left:0;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.05"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Project objectives</h2><ul class="text-xl text-text-secondary tight pl-6"><li class="reveal">Design a smart system to monitor hydrogen production, storage and transportation from a single software platform.</li><li class="reveal">Integrate renewable energy inputs and estimate hydrogen output automatically from operating data.</li><li class="reveal">Track tank status, pressure, quantity, dispatch schedule and delivery history.</li><li class="reveal">Provide dashboard analytics, alerts, authentication and report generation for administrators and operators.</li><li class="reveal">Present a Java-Swing-based academic prototype with database support and structured testing.</li></ul></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="5"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-70px;left:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;bottom:-50px;right:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas-ambient" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">System concept</h2><div class="ascii-box reveal">+----------------+     +------------------+     +------------------+
