"text-3xl">📄</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Reports</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Daily and monthly summaries.</div></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-xl p-4 reveal"><div class="text-3xl">🛠️</div><div class="font-bold mt-2">Admin</div><div class="mini text-text-secondary">Master data and control actions.</div></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="9"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:360px;height:360px;top:-70px;left:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-40px;right:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Functional requirements</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>User registration, login and role-based access.</li><li>Energy source entry and validation.</li><li>Hydrogen production calculation and history.</li><li>Storage tank monitoring and allocation.</li></ul></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><ul class="mini text-text-secondary tight pl-5"><li>Transport scheduling and dispatch logging.</li><li>Dashboard visualization and threshold alerts.</li><li>Search, filtering and report generation.</li><li>Admin controls for users, tanks and routes.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="10"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:340px;height:340px;top:-60px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.07"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-60px;left:-20px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.05"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Non-functional requirements</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-5"><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Security</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Secure login, data protection and access restrictions.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Performance</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Fast retrieval of dashboard and report data.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Reliability</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Stable operation with consistent calculations.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Scalability</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Extendable for more sensors, tanks and vehicles.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Availability</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Accessible to multiple users with minimal downtime.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-5 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Usability</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Simple GUI suitable for academic and lab users.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="11"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:360px;height:360px;top:-90px;right:-80px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:260px;height:260px;bottom:-50px;left:-50px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.07"></div></div><canvas class="particle-canvas-ambient" style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1" width="300" height="150"></canvas><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Architecture diagram</h2><div class="ascii-box reveal">Users/Admin --&gt; Java Swing GUI --&gt; Service Layer --&gt; JDBC --&gt; MySQL Database
