  <div class="slide" data-slide="12"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;top:-70px;left:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:230px;height:230px;bottom:-30px;right:-40px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Design diagrams</h2><table class="mini reveal"><tbody><tr><th>Diagram</th><th>Main purpose</th><th>Key elements</th></tr><tr><td>Use case</td><td>Shows actor interactions</td><td>Admin, operator, login, energy, reports</td></tr><tr><td>Class diagram</td><td>Represents object model</td><td>User, EnergySource, Production, Tank, Transport</td></tr><tr><td>Sequence diagram</td><td>Shows message flow</td><td>GUI, service, DB, response</td></tr><tr><td>DFD level 0/1</td><td>Shows system data movement</td><td>Inputs, processes, data stores, outputs</td></tr><tr><td>ER diagram</td><td>Shows database relations</td><td>PK, FK and entity links</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="13"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:330px;height:330px;top:-70px;right:-60px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.07"></div><div class="blob" style="width:240px;height:240px;bottom:-40px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Database schema</h2><div class="ascii-box reveal">users(user_id PK, username, password_hash, role, status)
energy_source(source_id PK, source_type, input_date, power_kwh, location)
hydrogen_production(prod_id PK, source_id FK, electrolyzer_type, efficiency, h2_kg)
storage_tank(tank_id PK, tank_name, capacity_kg, available_kg, pressure_bar, prod_id FK)
transport(trans_id PK, tank_id FK, vehicle_no, destination, dispatch_date, quantity_kg, status)
reports(report_id PK, generated_by FK-&gt;users.user_id, report_type, period_start, period_end, file_path)</div><p class="mt-4 text-text-secondary text-lg reveal">The schema keeps source data normalized and connects production, tank allocation and transport records through foreign keys.</p></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="14"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:350px;height:350px;top:-80px;left:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:220px;height:220px;bottom:-50px;right:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-3);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Core algorithms</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Login authentication</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Validate username, hash password, compare role and grant session if matched.</p><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-4 mb-2">H2 estimation</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Use renewable energy input, electrolyzer efficiency and conversion factor to estimate kg of hydrogen.</p></div><div class="bg-glass-bg backdrop-blur-xl border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6 reveal"><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Storage allocation</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Assign hydrogen to first suitable tank with available capacity and safe pressure margin.</p><h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-4 mb-2">Transport scheduling</h3><p class="mini text-text-secondary">Match destination demand, tank quantity, vehicle availability and delivery priority.</p></div></div></div></div>

  <div class="slide" data-slide="15"><div class="gradient-mesh"><div class="blob" style="width:360px;height:360px;top:-60px;right:-70px;background:var(--color-accent-2);opacity:.08"></div><div class="blob" style="width:250px;height:250px;bottom:-40px;left:-30px;background:var(--color-accent-1);opacity:.06"></div></div><div class="content"><h2 class="font-display text-5xl mb-6 reveal">Sample pseudocode</h2><div class="ascii-box reveal">Algorithm HydrogenProductionEstimation
Input: power_kwh, efficiency_percent
Output: hydrogen_kg
Begin
  usable_energy = power_kwh * (efficiency_percent / 100)
  hydrogen_kg = usable_energy / 50
  store hydrogen_kg in production table
  return hydrogen_kg
End

Algorithm StorageAllocation
Input: hydrogen_kg
For each tank in tank_list
  If tank.available_kg &gt;= hydrogen_kg and tank.pressure_bar &lt; threshold
     allocate tank
     update available_kg
